  core strength\, better posture and balance skills\, more physical and men
 tal energy\, and improved sports performance. A recording of each class is
  available on YouTube.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trum
 baEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1381777523
LOCATION:Matchbox Tarble Commons Upper Level
