SUMMARY:Swarthmore Send-Off in Seattle
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Reception\\nS
 warthmore Send-Off in Seattle Tuesday\, July 21 6–8 p.m. Kelsey Creek F
 arm410 130th Place SEBellevue Kindly register by July 13th This gathering 
 brings together alumni\, current students\, and families in Seattle to wel
 come you and other members of the Class of 2030\, along with your families
 \, as you begin your Swarthmore journey. This is a great opportunity to as
 k current students questions\, learn about life after Swarthmore from alum
 ni\, and make new friends before the start of school. Refreshments will be
  provided. Kindly register by Monday\, July 13. We hope to see you there! 
