SUMMARY:Swarthmore Send-Off: DMV
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Reception\\nS
 warthmore Send-Off: DMVSaturday\, August 1 2–4 p.m. Sandy Spring Friends
  Meeting17715 Meeting House RoadKindly register by Thursday\, July 23. Thi
 s gathering brings together alumni\, current students\, and families in th
 e DMV to welcome you\, other members of the Class of 2030\, and your famil
 ies as you begin your Swarthmore journey. This is a great opportunity to a
 sk questions of current students\, learn about life after Swarthmore from 
 alumni\, and make new friends before the start of school. Refreshments wil
 l be provided. We hope to see you there! Shanta Gyan P'28on behalf of the 
 Family Ambassador Program\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?t
 rumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1409084056
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1409084056
CATEGORIES:Reception
