SUMMARY:SwatMeets Philly
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Reception\\nS
 watMeets PhillyThursday\, August 13 5:30–7:30 p.m. Independence Beer Ga
 rden100 S. Independence Mall WestPhiladelphia SwatMeets are casual gatheri
 ngs designed to help you connect with fellow Swatties — those you know a
 nd those you’re soon to know. Whether you’ve called the city home for 
 years or just arrived\, this is your chance to join a welcoming community 
 of alumni who share that unmistakable Swarthmore energy. There’s no prog
 ram\, no pressure\, and no need to dress up. Come as you are\, stay as lon
 g as you like\, and leave with new connections. RSVP now! We can't wait to
  see you there! Katee Kemether ’23on behalf of the Swarthmore Alumni Cou
 ncil\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Deve
 nt%26eventid%3D1411230910
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1411230910
CATEGORIES:Reception
END:VEVENT
