SUMMARY:Swarthmore at the Dodgers
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Recreation-Ge
 neral\\nDodger Stadium1000 Vin Scully AveLos Angeles\, CA 90012 Join fello
 w alums for a great day at the ballpark. Connect with old friends\, make n
 ew connections\, and bring your Garnet spirit to the stands. Before the fi
 rst pitch\, we’ll host a casual meetup inside the stadium. It’s the pe
 rfect chance to grab a snack\, catch up\, and mingle with your local commu
 nity. Your alumni host\, Grant Torre ’17\, will be there to welcome you.
  We’ll host a casual meetup inside the stadium before the first pitch. I
 t’s the perfect chance to grab a snack\, catch up\, and mingle with your
  local community. Your alumni host\, Grant Torre ’17\, will be there to 
 welcome you. Program: Pre-Game Meetup: 12:15–1 p.m. (specific stadium lo
 cation details to follow) Game Time: 1:10 p.m. vs. Pirates What to Wear: Y
 our favorite Swarthmore gear Important Ticket Information: Tickets for thi
 s event are entirely electronic. They will be securely distributed directl
 y to you through the MLB Ballpark app exactly one week before the game. Pl
 ease review the official stadium policies on bags and entry before you arr
 ive.  Secure your tickets and get ready for game day! All ticket sales ar
 e final\; no refunds will be issued. Please contact us at alumni@swarthmor
 e.edu with any questions before purchasing.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral
 .swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1411230911
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1411230911
CATEGORIES:Recreation-General
END:VEVENT
